Title: A Fishy Gift
Description:
Murglgalgul!

Glulmual, rluu glua ffrl wawawamual. Lalala!

Mowua ha mwaaay.

<Murloc You raises a fish up in both of $Ghis:her:their; hands towards you. It seems very officious. Soridormi may want to see this.>
ObjectivesText: After completing a Time Rift, return to Soridormi in the Tyrhold Reservoir.
